{"tid":828639,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【租都要跌】太古城租金回到2016年 3房劈租7,000元","createTime":"2018-09-19T23:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T00:57:23.000Z","uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"73c3aa3b69144ca46c75140cfcae27d052caf87b","tid":828639,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180919/large/1537354342_2881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180919%2Flarge%2F1537354342_2881.jpg&h=07c751f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中原地產趙鴻運表示，鰂魚涌太古城買賣淡靜，9月僅1宗買賣，租務成交卻錄得20餘宗，平均實用呎租43元。屋苑亦出現一宗劈租個案，為青松閣低層C室，實用面積897方呎，3房連套房間隔，向東南，望開揚園景。業主7月暑假旺季前叫租4萬元，後見租客背景良好，起租期快，最終減價7,000元以3.3萬元租出，減幅17.5%，呎租僅36.8元。<br />\n<br />\n趙鴻運續稱，上址對上租約為2016年12月，當時月租3.3萬元，意味新租金回到近兩年前水平。春櫻閣低層F室，面積相同，今年2月以4.7萬元租出，呎租52.4元，但此單位附設60萬元裝修及家電齊全。景觀則以青松閣望內園較清靜為佳。<br />\n<br />\n業主2010年8月以860萬元買入單位，一直作收租用途，租金回報4.6厘。"},{"pid":"a8b0a62309516548b5d70b40522bce9d8f342bb7","tid":828639,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:56:05.000Z","msg":"做乜唔加租？"},{"pid":"5de034c37a0f503d0ef585ca4a6593b777e7333a","tid":828639,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:57:18.000Z","msg":"租金唔計"},{"pid":"4dfecd5795e206204ff696562ac524fa60643dfc","tid":828639,"uid":922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8b0a62309516548b5d70b40522bce9d8f342bb7","tid":828639,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:56:05.000Z","msg":"做乜唔加租？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:58:42.000Z","msg":"業主好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369ec64eca8e3a03ff25ccb4fd422c62c54f37bf","tid":828639,"uid":93100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73c3aa3b69144ca46c75140cfcae27d052caf87b","tid":828639,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"